Packages 
Package Description
hrps
The common package contains the common classes used by HRPS.
hrps.boundary
The package that contains classes handling the execution of business logics of entity and present the result as a response to the client.
hrps.control
This package contains classes that encapsulates the business logic and the business rules.
hrps.entity
This package contains classes that represent domain objects.
hrps.entity.enums
This package contains enumerations that is used for the entities.
hrps.exception
This package contains the exception classes that are specially defined for the HRPS.
tool
An utility package that is used to do file IO operations with Serializable opearations
